snippet.title: KaiserPunk - Official Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at alpha gameplay from Kaiserpunk in this latest trailer for the upcoming city builder and grand strategy game set in an alternative 20th-century world. The trailer gives a brief overview of the gameplay elements of Kaiserpunk, including city building, grand strategy, production, logistics, and choices. Kaiserpunk will be available on Steam.

In Kaiserpunk, engage in epic battles on land, sea, and air, or use your economic power to emerge as the ultimate victor.

#IGN #Gaming
